## DR Runbook
1. **Pre-Failover**: Verify DynamoDB Global Tables replication status in both regions
2. **Execute Failover**: Run Step Function or manually update Global Accelerator endpoint weights
3. **Post-Failover**: Confirm API health via /health endpoint in DR region
4. **Rollback**: Trigger rollback Step Function when SLA recovers

